item.title: How to Come off the Bench in Basketball
item.description:
How to Come off the Bench in Basketball | Sports Psychology Podcast

In this episode, you will learn how to stay locked in on the bench. We discuss how to stay focused to enter the game off the bench so you are ready to play.

Dr. Patrick Cohn is a master mental performance coach who works with professional athletes at Peak Performance Sports, LLC. ​​ Improve your mindset for sports with our certified mental performance coaches. Learn more at peaksports.com... Feed: https://sportspsychology.libsyn.com/rss
